<ul><li><strong>Cinematic Effects:</strong> Includes lighting simulation, slow-motion, and camera tracking.</li></ul>
<ul><li><strong>AI Editing:</strong> Users can issue natural language commands such as <em>â€œadd dramatic sunsetâ€</em> or <em>â€œincrease brightness.â€</em></li></ul>
